    {
      "id": "1525841012616990820",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-07-12T12:27:26.163+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "(1) we don't even have enough info about the open process to generate the mask. Sometimes we don't even know what those masks are.\n(2) Even if we did, there is no way the foundry would even let you ... a bad mask could cause issues bringing their production line down.",
